# IPv4 loopback
127.0.0.1
127.0.0.1:*
http://127.0.0.1*
https://127.0.0.1*

# All interfaces
0.0.0.0
0.0.0.0:*

# Local DNS
*.local
*.localhost

# IPv6 loopback
::1
\[::1\]
\[::1\]:*

